snippet.title: Amber's Story Trailer 2006
snippet.description:
True story about Amber Hagerman who was 9 years old when she was abducted while riding her bicycle, prompting her mother to seek out a system that alerts the nation of abducted children, we know that to be called an Amber Alert today. Ambers Story commercial is after the news report. 
Directed By: Keoni Waxman
Cast: Elisabeth Röhm, Teryl Rothery, Myron Natwick, Sophie Hough, Jodelle Ferland, Zak Ludwig, Tim Henry, Karen Austin, Antony Holland, Michael Adamthwaite, Greg Michaels, Malcolm Scott, Mitchell Kosterman, Claude Knowlton, James Purcell
https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0840999/
